  "texts": [
    "After the initial data cleaning, which involved removing special characters and adjusting the format, the data underwent extraction of key attributes and a thorough review process.",
    "This step included the assessment of information by both machine algorithms and experts in TCM.",
    "The extracted key attributes were then used to form the final dataset, ensuring both accuracy and security.",
    "Subsequently, we employed ChatGLM for data augmentation, further enhancing the dataset size to improve the model's performance.",
    "Finally, we fine-tuned the foundation model, ChatGLM-6B, using the PEFT method, resulting in the CPMI-ChatGLM model."
  ],
